quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Ndayira Malayika ezisikambula emyoyo gy’abajeemu mu bukambwe
  79,2,Era ndayira Malayika ezisowola emyoyo gy’abakkiriza obusowozi
  79,3,Era ndayira Malayika eziwugira mu bbanga oluwuga
  79,4,Era ndayira Malayika ezivuganya oluvuganya nga zitwala emyoyo gy’abakkiriza mu jjana
  79,5,Ne ndayira ne Malayika ezissa mu nkola ebiragiro (Byange)
  79,6,(Mukimanye nti ebitonde byonna bigenda kuzikirira) ku lunaku buli kintu kyonna lwe kirikankana nga engombe efuuyiddwa
  79,7,Luligobererwa olufuuwa olw'okubiri (olw'okuzuukira)
  79,8,E mitima gy’abatakkiriza ku lunaku olwo giribeera mu kutya
  79,9,Amaaso gaabwe nga makkakkamu
  79,10,"Bagamba (nga bajerega), nti \"Mazima ddala tulizzibwawo mu bulamu nga bwetulimu kati"
  79,11,Bwe tuliba tumaze okufuuka amagumba amamerengufu
  79,12,Bongerako ne bagamba nti (okwonno bwekiriba bwekityo) kuliba kudda kwa kufaafaaganirwa
  79,13,Mazima okuzuukira lugenda kubeera olukanga lumu lwokka
  79,14,Baligenda okulaba nga bali ku ngulu ku nsi
  79,15,Abaffe wamanya ku kyafaayo kya Nabbi Musa
  79,16,Awo Katonda we yakoowoolera Musa nga (Musa) ali mu lusenyi olutukuvu 'Tuwa
  79,17,N'amugamba nti genda eri Firaawo kubanga ye asusse mu bujeemu ne mu buwakanyi
  79,18,"Omugambe nti, Abaffe waalyetaaze okwetukuza (n'okkiriza mukama Katonda wo)"
  79,19,Ndyoke mbe nga nkulungamya eri Katonda wo obeere nga omutya
  79,20,(Nabbi Musa) n’alaga Firaawo obujulizi obwenkukunala
  79,21,(Firaawo) naalimbisa era n’ajeema
  79,22,Bwe yamala n'abikuba amabega era n’akola kaweefube w'okubirwanyisa
  79,23,"N’akungaanya (amagye ge, abakungu be, n’abalogo) n’alangirira"
  79,24,Ng’agamba nti nze Katonda wa mmwe owa waggulu
  79,25,Katonda n’amubonereza n’okumuzikiriza olw’ekisobyo ekyasembayo n’ekyasooka
  79,26,Mazima mu ekyo (eky’okuzikiriza Firaawo) mulimu eky’okulabirako eri oyo atya Katonda